sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as site:list
    participant Scanner as SiteScanner
    participant Config as ConfigManager
    participant DB as DatabaseService

    User->>CLI: run site:list
    CLI->>Scanner: scan()

    Scanner->>Config: get paths + overrides
    Scanner->>DB: get PHP version per site
    Scanner-->>CLI: sites

    CLI->>Config: get TLD + default PHP
    CLI-->>User: JSON or table output
